<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:09:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>斯塔默和马克龙本周无法给拜登的一条关键建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-one-critical-piece-of-advice-starmer-and-macron-cant-give-biden-this-week/00000190-9293-dfc0-a3f3-bef388390000</link><description>政治命运截然不同、选举环境截然不同的三个亲密盟友将于本周在华盛顿举行的北约会议上会面。联盟的未来取决于对美国总统的政治建议，而英法领导人却无法真正提供这些建议</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-one-critical-piece-of-advice-starmer-and-macron-cant-give-biden-this-week/00000190-9293-dfc0-a3f3-bef388390000</guid></item><item><title>模棱两可的规定让骑警可以自行决定鞭打以色列抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ambiguous-regulations-let-mounted-police-whip-israeli-protesters-at-their-discretion/00000190-9241-d1c5-a1d6-bacd20500000</link><description>在过去的一年半里，马匹和骑警造成了数十名抗议者受伤。当司法部审问一名涉嫌鞭打抗议者的警官时，警方发布了新规定，允许当骑警意识到自己或公众的安全受到威胁时，可以使用缰绳攻击抗议者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ambiguous-regulations-let-mounted-police-whip-israeli-protesters-at-their-discretion/00000190-9241-d1c5-a1d6-bacd20500000</guid></item><item><title>厄立特里亚人在特拉维夫南部斗殴中丧生，这是自去年九月骚乱以来第七人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/eritrean-killed-in-brawl-in-south-tel-aviv-the-seventh-killed-since-riots-last-september/00000190-927c-dfc0-a3f3-befd7fe00000</link><description>厄立特里亚政权支持者和反对者之间出于政治动机的冲突已造成 150 多人受伤。与此同时，耶路撒冷法官上个月裁定，厄立特里亚军队的逃兵可能成为在以色列获得庇护的理由</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 14:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/eritrean-killed-in-brawl-in-south-tel-aviv-the-seventh-killed-since-riots-last-september/00000190-927c-dfc0-a3f3-befd7fe00000</guid></item><item><title>“一个奇迹般的时刻”：以色列极右翼犹太原教旨主义者想要战争、定居点和起义。内塔尼亚胡正在为他们提供便利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-miraculous-time-israels-far-right-fundamentalists-want-war-settlements-and-intifada/00000190-917b-d591-a7ff-fffbc46e0000</link><description>对于像奥里特·斯特罗克和比扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇这样的极右翼弥赛亚定居者部长及其大批选民来说，加沙九个月的战斗还不够。他们感觉到了征服和权力的圣经机会，内塔尼亚胡总理不会公开反对他们。这是两个以色列人之间战争的故事</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-miraculous-time-israels-far-right-fundamentalists-want-war-settlements-and-intifada/00000190-917b-d591-a7ff-fffbc46e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟提出允许以色列古物管理局在西岸开展业务的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/coalition-advances-bill-allowing-israels-antiquities-authority-to-operate-in-west-bank/00000190-91e4-d3a3-ad9a-b3ff1c630000</link><description>该法案的解释性说明称，“毫无疑问，这些地区沉浸在犹太历史中，无论如何，这些发现与巴勒斯坦权力机构没有历史或其他联系。”古物管理局局长反对此举并表示不可行</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 11:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/coalition-advances-bill-allowing-israels-antiquities-authority-to-operate-in-west-bank/00000190-91e4-d3a3-ad9a-b3ff1c630000</guid></item><item><title>“外交炸弹”：以色列侨民部长支持勒庞，以色列外交官愤怒不已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-rallied-behind-le-pen-and-israeli-diplomats-are-livid/00000190-918b-d443-adbe-b1dbca120000</link><description>接受《国土报》采访的以色列外交部官员表示，奇克利部长损害了与法国的关系，其中一位官员表示，他在与欧洲极右翼政党不断发展的关系中完全独立运作</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:14:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-rallied-behind-le-pen-and-israeli-diplomats-are-livid/00000190-918b-d443-adbe-b1dbca120000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：甘茨保持领先内塔尼亚胡，反对派集团有望获得多数席位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/poll-gantz-maintains-lead-over-netanyahu-opposition-bloc-poised-for-majority/00000190-90f8-d99b-a5fc-9ffd227e0000</link><description>反对派集团预计将获得 67 个席位，而内塔尼亚胡的联盟集团预计将获得 53 个席位</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 06:25:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/poll-gantz-maintains-lead-over-netanyahu-opposition-bloc-poised-for-majority/00000190-90f8-d99b-a5fc-9ffd227e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军医务人员在加沙受重伤；黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-live/idf-suspicious-target-intercepted-over-red-sea-en-route-to-israel/00000190-904c-de32-a79e-9fdda67f0000</link><description>以色列国防军称，它摧毁了位于加沙市舒贾耶耶附近的哈马斯总部 ■ 以色列国防军称，它杀死了真主党火箭和导弹部队的一名成员 ■ 美联社报道称，尽管辛瓦尔不情愿，但加沙的哈马斯官员仍敦促海外领导人寻求达成协议 ■ 哈马斯称，以色列国防军下令加沙城 Al-Ahli 阿拉伯医院的疏散 ■ 以色列国防军称，部队在加沙城近东救济工程处大院执行任务，为平民建立了安全通道 ■ 以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:23:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article-live/idf-suspicious-target-intercepted-over-red-sea-en-route-to-israel/00000190-904c-de32-a79e-9fdda67f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在以色列与哈马斯的谈判中争取时间，押注人质的命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-approach-to-negotiations-is-to-stall-gambling-on-the-hostages-fate/00000190-8e8e-d591-a7ff-fefeb1570000</link><description>美国对埃及和卡塔尔的压力正推动与哈马斯取得突破。然而，内塔尼亚胡在代表团访问开罗之前采取了一贯的强硬立场。拜登的健康状况可能会转移人们对中东的注意力</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-approach-to-negotiations-is-to-stall-gambling-on-the-hostages-fate/00000190-8e8e-d591-a7ff-fefeb1570000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与哈马斯重启谈判，公布人质交易“原则清单”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publishes-list-of-principles-for-hostage-deal-as-talks-with-hamas-renew/00000190-8eb4-d0cb-abb9-feb7f0a00000</link><description>外交消息人士对内塔尼亚胡的声明表示担忧，称总理“限制了自己和谈判团队”，但另一位消息人士指出“谈判中出现了真正的安全担忧”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 19:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publishes-list-of-principles-for-hostage-deal-as-talks-with-hamas-renew/00000190-8eb4-d0cb-abb9-feb7f0a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府出人意料地宣布建立以色列第一家阿拉伯文化博物馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/in-surprise-move-netanyahu-government-announces-israels-first-museum-of-arab-culture/00000190-8dd6-dcf1-afdd-ddf6a0e70000</link><description>以色列北部的 Umm al-Fahm 美术馆的目标之一是向游客介绍巴勒斯坦的叙事，该美术馆将在未来五年内获得 2200 万谢克尔（近 600 万美元），以达到国家博物馆标准</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:50:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/in-surprise-move-netanyahu-government-announces-israels-first-museum-of-arab-culture/00000190-8dd6-dcf1-afdd-ddf6a0e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的阿拉伯公民是否应该应征入伍——不是加入以色列国防军，而是服兵役？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/should-israels-arab-citizens-be-drafted-into-civilian-national-service/00000190-8d98-d591-a7ff-fffaf0780000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡联盟努力解决极端正统犹太人的兵役问题时，另一个主要社区免受以色列国防军征兵的约束：阿拉伯公民。尽管阿拉伯领导人对民用替代方案充满热情，但他们并不相信政府的意图。一位活动人士问道：“这个法西斯政府是否希望将我视为以色列成功故事的一部分？”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/should-israels-arab-citizens-be-drafted-into-civilian-national-service/00000190-8d98-d591-a7ff-fffaf0780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在加沙南部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-southern-gaza/00000190-8e29-d0cb-abb9-fe3bac970000</link><description>来自以色列北部德鲁兹村庄的 25 岁贾拉·易卜拉欣 (Jalaa Ibrahem) 少校周日在加沙地带被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-southern-gaza/00000190-8e29-d0cb-abb9-fe3bac970000</guid></item><item><title>英国新首相与以色列内塔尼亚胡通话，呼吁停火和人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/u-k-s-new-pm-speaks-with-israels-netanyahu-calls-for-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/00000190-8dca-d591-a7ff-fffa76c90000</link><description>以色列总理凯尔·斯塔默表示，他对以色列北部边境的局势感到“担忧” ■ 新当选的总理还与巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯进行了交谈</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/u-k-s-new-pm-speaks-with-israels-netanyahu-calls-for-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/00000190-8dca-d591-a7ff-fffa76c90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列和内塔尼亚胡的看法已经过时，这是一个问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-07/ty-article/.highlight/biden-is-out-of-date-on-israel-and-netanyahu-and-its-a-problem/00000190-8dc0-d0cb-abb9-fff327b00000</link><description>作为一名经常撰写有关美以关系文章的以色列记者，有一件事是明确的：拜登对以色列政治的理解属于 20 世纪 80 年代，而不是当前时刻</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-07/ty-article/.highlight/biden-is-out-of-date-on-israel-and-netanyahu-and-its-a-problem/00000190-8dc0-d0cb-abb9-fff327b00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与以色列国防部长就豁免极端正统派参军法案发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israels-defense-minister-clash-over-bill-exempting-ultra-orthodox-from-army/00000190-8ddd-de32-a79e-9fdd32cd0000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡等人与以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特就延长义务兵役期限和反对豁免极端正统派加入以色列国防军等问题展开激烈讨论</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 16:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israels-defense-minister-clash-over-bill-exempting-ultra-orthodox-from-army/00000190-8ddd-de32-a79e-9fdd32cd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 275 天：埃及将接待以色列和美国代表团进行停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-275-egypt-to-host-israeli-u-s-delegations-for-truce-talks/00000190-8df4-d0cb-abb9-fff7781e0001</link><description>据报道，埃及将接待以色列和美国代表团，讨论人质释放谈判中的“突出问题” ■ 消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列周末提出了新要求，预计将推迟达成可能的协议 ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了 50 多枚火箭弹 ■ 数千人参加以色列各地针对人质交易和提​​前选举举行为期一天的抗议活动 ■ 战争进入 275 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 16:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-275-egypt-to-host-israeli-u-s-delegations-for-truce-talks/00000190-8df4-d0cb-abb9-fff7781e0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列检方反对内塔尼亚胡推迟腐败审判证词的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-prosecution-objects-to-netanyahus-request-to-postpone-corruption-trial-testimony/00000190-8d58-d443-adbe-ad5ab6740000</link><description>检方希望审判不晚于 11 月继续进行。法官现在需要审查双方的请求，并定于周二就此事举行听证会</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 14:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-prosecution-objects-to-netanyahus-request-to-postpone-corruption-trial-testimony/00000190-8d58-d443-adbe-ad5ab6740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家劳工法庭裁定同性伴侣的男性可以被定义为家庭主妇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-national-labor-court-rules-man-in-same-sex-partnership-can-be-defined-as-homemaker/00000190-8d58-d5d5-a1b5-8d78600c0000</link><description>法院裁定，保险法中仅使用“家庭主妇”一词的男性和女性之间的语言区别是歧视性的，并且基于古老的世界观</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 13:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-national-labor-court-rules-man-in-same-sex-partnership-can-be-defined-as-homemaker/00000190-8d58-d5d5-a1b5-8d78600c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列缺乏战后加沙计划可能会加剧停火反对者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-an-israeli-plan-for-postwar-gaza-could-boost-cease-fire-opponents/00000190-8ce0-dd37-a5f7-bee2a2120000</link><description>如果没有其他选择，哈马斯官员可能会在停火达成后控制加沙 ■ 如果以色列不做出决定，建立军事政权将提上议程</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 12:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-an-israeli-plan-for-postwar-gaza-could-boost-cease-fire-opponents/00000190-8ce0-dd37-a5f7-bee2a2120000</guid></item></channel></rss>